<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 19:42:58 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>夏日傍晚</title><link>https://some.pics/6a42cabfcb24c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;夏天的傍晚。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An old city building with a very unique facade and a tower. Entrance to a city train station in front. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a42cabfcb24c.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 19:42:58 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a42966ad4ecb</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Zalman Schachter-Shalomi 和 Ram Das，约2016年&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two smiling elder mystics." height="960" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/gtdandy/6a42966ad4ecb.jpg" width="1280"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://gtdandy.some.pics"&gt;@gtdandy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 15:59:41 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a428bf324459</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我姐姐在亚利桑那州天堂谷的房子里的照片。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A sunset with two palm trees." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/gtdandy/6a428bf324459.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://gtdandy.some.pics"&gt;@gtdandy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 15:15:02 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4233d626d0a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;外部内部
#无滤镜&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="One pane of the double-glazed window is open towards the room; the rest of the window is concealed behind a curtain. The blue sky and green trees outside are reflected in the glass and are the only colours in the otherwise dark and monochrome room. " height="2800" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a4233d626d0a.jpg" width="2800"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 08:59:05 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>石雕狮头守望老街</title><link>https://some.pics/6a422539acca0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一个石雕狮头，鬃毛飘逸，从历史城区建筑的外立面上俯瞰街道。这是一件小巧的建筑艺术品，静静地经受住了时间的考验。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Stone lion carving with a majestic, flowing mane and a serious expression. The detailed texture conveys strength and timelessness." height="4360" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a422539acca0.jpg" width="3270"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 07:56:45 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>